name: Shadow
description:
5th full length alt-electronic release from Darling Coils // First physical NFT crossover release with development by computereveryday.

  ~Any purchase of this interactive album NFT includes physical copy of one associated edition of the album~  

I will need a mailing address to complete this transaction. Please message me on twitter @darling_coils after purchase. The 50 available NFTs have a 1:1 availability with the associated cassettes.

computereveryday is a generative artist and fellow savr gang member who’s been making waves in the NFT world market space. Check out computereveryday on hicetnunc.xyz/computereveryday and follow him on twitter @computerevryday
